params.prompt: ^character^ A photorealistic, cinematic image of a male rap artist standing in front of a massive, surreal hourglass filled with glowing golden sand particles. The hourglass towers over the artist, fully visible in the background, with its crystalline surface reflecting faint highlights of light. The golden sand inside flows dynamically, glowing as it cascades downward in slow motion. Ethereal clouds and wisps of smoke swirl gently around the hourglass, adding a surreal, dreamlike quality.  The artist is positioned at the center of the composition in a full-body shot, exuding confidence in a stylish, modern outfit. He wears a fitted black leather jacket with subtle textured detailing, layered over a charcoal gray turtleneck. Dark fitted jeans complement his look, paired with sleek black high-top sneakers with metallic accents. The ensemble balances urban edge with sophistication, highlighting his charisma and presence. His posture is grounded and steady, with his arms relaxed at his sides. His head is slightly tilted forward, and his piercing amber-brown eyes lock onto the viewer with quiet determination. His jet-black locs, styled half-up and half-down with faint golden-brown highlights, frame his face and shoulders, adding to his distinct, polished aesthetic.  The background beyond the hourglass and visual elements fades into deep black with a soft blur, creating a stark contrast that draws attention to the glowing hourglass, the swirling smoke, and the artist’s figure. The cracked concrete floor beneath the artist subtly reflects the golden light from the sand and adds texture to the otherwise minimalist setting.  The lighting is dramatic and cinematic, with a soft overhead glow illuminating the artist and hourglass. The golden sand radiates warm light, which contrasts beautifully against the cool tones of the surrounding smoke and the pure blackness beyond. The centered composition ensures the full height of both the artist and the hourglass is in view, creating a visually powerful and striking image.

params.prompt: ^character^ A surreal, photorealistic scene of an artist walking forward through a wide, open corridor surrounded by floating time symbols—hourglasses, clocks, and watch faces—suspended weightlessly in the air. The time symbols pulse faintly with golden and silver light, their rhythmic glow casting soft reflections onto the smooth, dark floor below. The atmosphere is heavy, with a mix of warm and cool tones creating a balance between tension and determination.  Glowing threads of light coil gently around the artist’s neck and shoulders, pulling back slightly as if resisting their movement. The threads shimmer with golden and amber hues, their faint glow illuminating the artist’s figure. The artist, dressed in a fitted black hoodie with the hood pulled back, strides forward with quiet determination, their body slightly tense from the strain of the threads holding them back.   With each step forward, the threads begin to dissolve into golden particles that scatter and float upward, symbolizing the gradual breaking of constraints. As the threads weaken, the floating clocks and hourglasses subtly shift their positions, some aligning and glowing more brightly, symbolizing the artist's growing control over the passage of time.   Soft ambient light highlights the glowing threads, while shadows stretch long and backward from the artist’s movements, emphasizing the tension between progress and restraint. The corridor fades into abstract darkness at the edges, keeping the focus on the interplay of light, time symbols, and the artist’s journey forward.

params.prompt: ^character^ A surreal, photorealistic scene of an artist standing in an abstract, shadowy space filled with floating, distorted clocks and timepieces. The artist faces the camera, their posture tense, as a rhythmic, glowing pulse radiates outward from their chest. Each pulse creates visible ripples in the air, bending and distorting the floating clocks nearby. The clocks, some vintage and others modern, stretch and twist unnaturally as the waves pass through them, their faces freezing momentarily before resuming their slow, erratic ticking.  The artist, wearing a fitted black hoodie with the hood pulled back, clutches their chest briefly, their expression conveying both tension and determination. From their chest, warm golden light pulses in sync with their heartbeat, casting dynamic highlights and shadows across their figure and the nearby clocks. The ripples in the air shimmer with faint hues of gold and silver, emphasizing the surreal distortion.  As the tension peaks, the artist exhales softly, releasing a glowing, ethereal mist that dissipates into the surrounding space. The ripples gradually calm, and the floating clocks begin to stabilize, though faint distortions linger as a reminder of the pressure’s impact. The background remains abstract and cool-toned, with swirls of soft blue and gray mist contrasting against the warm, radiant light emanating from the artist’s chest, symbolizing their resilience amidst the suffocating pressure of time and expectation.
